  "detailed_description": "Snake Blocks is a 3D puzzle game about snakes! You must weave a group of colorful snakes through over 50 hand-crafted levels, until you've found a way to bring them all to their respective destinations. With Snake Blocks' four game modes of ever-increasing difficulty, you'll find yourself snaking for hours!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut wait, there's more! Snake Blocks comes with a built-in level designer, so you can create your own puzzles. Steam workshop support coming soon!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSnake Blocks is playable on PC, Mac, and is coming soon to Linux!",
  "about_the_game": "Snake Blocks is a 3D puzzle game about snakes! You must weave a group of colorful snakes through over 50 hand-crafted levels, until you've found a way to bring them all to their respective destinations. With Snake Blocks' four game modes of ever-increasing difficulty, you'll find yourself snaking for hours!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut wait, there's more! Snake Blocks comes with a built-in level designer, so you can create your own puzzles. Steam workshop support coming soon!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSnake Blocks is playable on PC, Mac, and is coming soon to Linux!",
